        "created_at": "2025-03-05T23:23:37.328Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This just happened to me as well when I updated to 7.45 on Windows! Except I’m getting Russian (and it says that my “system language” is English), which is slightly disconcerting. In a way it’s slightly less disturbing if other people are getting other languages…?</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/f/d/fdc8989de71128e84bf353eebdde3ebc76e60eba.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/fdc8989de71128e84bf353eebdde3ebc76e60eba\" title=\"language\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/d/fdc8989de71128e84bf353eebdde3ebc76e60eba_2_690x269.png\" alt=\"language\" data-base62-sha1=\"Ad4zFvcBBzW548kjkuowNzjtDVE\" width=\"690\" height=\"269\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/d/fdc8989de71128e84bf353eebdde3ebc76e60eba_2_690x269.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/f/d/fdc8989de71128e84bf353eebdde3ebc76e60eba.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/f/d/fdc8989de71128e84bf353eebdde3ebc76e60eba.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"232324\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">language</span><span class=\"informations\">873×341 25.9 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>PS: I have also uninstalled/reinstalled and rebooted to no avail. I do have Russian input method installed on my system but I have never installed anything with Russian as the default language.</p>",
